at this courthouse. . .

546
01:03:10,182 --> 01:03:13,644
. . .that Christine Sullivan's killer
will be tried.

547
01:03:14,437 --> 01:03:17,190
As you know, I came from
an impoverished family. . .

548
01:03:18,274 --> 01:03:20,568
...in an impoverished town.

549
01:03:21,861 --> 01:03:23,446
We lived with our doors...

550
01:03:23,821 --> 01:03:25,323
...unlocked.

551
01:03:26,365 --> 01:03:28,868
We all lock our doors now.

552
01:03:29,285 --> 01:03:31,829
-That's not what concerns me.
-A ginger ale.

553
01:03:32,038 --> 01:03:34,332
