01:15:17,660 --> 01:15:19,787
It's Kate calling.

695
01:15:19,996 --> 01:15:24,000
I was wondering
if you could call me, please.

696
01:15:25,209 --> 01:15:29,171
There's some things I'd like
to talk with you about...

697
01:15:29,380 --> 01:15:32,842
