if that's possible.

698
01:15:33,092 --> 01:15:34,385
Okay?

699
01:15:34,969 --> 01:15:38,139
Thanks and talk to you soon. Bye.

700
01:15:42,560 --> 01:15:43,769
Dad, hi.

701
01:15:43,978 --> 01:15:46,105
It's Kate calling.

702
01:15:46,355 --> 01:15:50,651
I was wondering
if you could call me, please.

703
01:15:51,569 --> 01:15:55,448
There's some things I'd like
to talk with you about...

704
01:15:55,698 --> 01:15:57,074
...and maybe even get together.

705
01:16:22,016 --> 01:16:25,520
So you all know where and when
