706
01:16:25,770 --> 01:16:27,605
He's slippery. He's an eel.

707
01:16:27,855 --> 01:16:29,982
He gets a whiff of a cop,
he disappears.

708
01:16:30,233 --> 01:16:32,193
Nobody moves until I order you.

709
01:16:32,860 --> 01:16:34,278
Then we move in on him.

710
01:16:34,529 --> 01:16:38,991
Expect Whitney to show up at 4.
His daughter will be waiting for him.

711
01:16:39,200 --> 01:16:41,869
It's important to stay
in your positions. . .

712
01:16:42,119 --> 01:16:44,914
. . .until you hear the order
to move in on him.

713
01:17:17,572 --> 01:17:18,447
Here you go.

714
01:17:18,656 --> 01:17:20,366
Could I have some cream?

715
01:17:37,592 --> 01:17:39,719
Gather around, gentlemen.

716
01:17:40,678 --> 01:17:43,306
Nobody moves till
the suspect's in place.

717
01:17:43,556 --> 01:17:45,016
Any questions?

718
01:17:45,558 --> 01:17:47,435
See you at the Alonzo.

719
01:17:48,060 --> 01:17:49,103
Boss is grateful.

720
01:17:49,312 --> 01:17:51,856
He'd appreciate
an eyewitness at the capture.

721
01:17:52,106 --> 01:17:54,108
This is our guy.

722
01:17:54,400 --> 01:17:57,528
If he isn't, he sure disappeared fast.
See you there.

723
01:19:22,613 --> 01:19:23,990
Tums?

724
01:19:25,074 --> 01:19:26,492
I got my own.

725
01:19:48,014 --> 01:19:49,640
Come on, Kate.

726
01:19:50,057 --> 01:19:52,560
-She gonna show?
-Yeah, she'll be here.

727
